---
title: Thai Style Peanut Chicken and Veggie Gyoza Noodles with Green Beans and Pepper
description: Ready in less than 25 minutes, these Thai Style Peanut Chicken and Veggie Gyoza Noodles have it all. Combining peanut butter with soy, ketjap manis and yellow Thai style paste results in a lightly spiced and flavoursome sauce to toss with noodles, veg and chicken.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF221018_R16_W48_UK_R12588-4_MB_Main_low-1e59a9f1.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/66db1a17313561920cf87c46-en-GB.pdf
author: HelloFresh
cuisine: Thai
servings: 2
course: main course
